|---------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|
| QUANTUM       | ROCK1/2 selectivity + Kv1 + N-type Ca + α2δ + β3-AR + GABA-B VQE       | F-novel-sci-Q-N            |
| WEAVE         | intrathecal pump scaffold + cell carrier + ECM bridging hydrogel       | F-novel-sci-W-N            |
