| RIBOZYME      | SOD1 + tofersen pattern ASO 척수 segment + neurotrophin mRNA            | F-novel-sci-RB-N           |
| NANOBOT       | spinal-cord-homing + lesion-targeted axon regeneration nanobot         | F-novel-sci-NB-N           |

