- F-disease-sci-Q-2: Kv1 + dalfampridine + 4-AP pocket VQE
- F-disease-sci-Q-3: N-type Ca + ziconotide intrathecal binding VQE
- F-disease-sci-Q-4: α2δ + gabapentin / pregabalin pocket VQE
- F-disease-sci-Q-5: β3-AR + vibegron vs mirabegron neurogenic OAB selectivity VQE
- F-disease-sci-Q-6: GABA-B + baclofen intrathecal pocket VQE
- F-disease-sci-Q-7: SNAP-25 / VAMP + 6 BoNT serotype binding VQE (oA/aboA/incoA/praboA/daxiboA/rimaboB)
- F-disease-sci-Q-8: 30-SCI drug library ranking
- F-disease-sci-W-1: intrathecal pump + ECM bridging hydrogel scaffold
